            <title><![CDATA[[衰]#男子患胃癌一查一家5口全感染幽门螺杆菌# 感染幽门螺杆菌后，会出现慢性胃炎、胃溃疡等疾病，出现胃痛、胃胀、恶心、反酸、消化不良等不适症状。但从目前的...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%82%A3%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B65%E5%8F%A3%E5%85%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%82%A3%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B65%E5%8F%A3%E5%85%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#男子患胃癌一查一家5口全感染幽门螺杆菌#</span></a> 感染幽门螺杆菌后，会出现慢性胃炎、胃溃疡等疾病，出现胃痛、胃胀、恶心、反酸、消化不良等不适症状。但从目前的研究看，只有10%到20%的人会出现消化道溃疡，而出现胃癌的比例就更低了，只有1%，因此，不需要过度焦虑。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[摊手]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_tanshou-fa05d4eacf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>远离幽门螺杆菌，请记好<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[奥特曼]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_aoteman-7ddbc90d1c.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br>✅餐具消毒、分餐；<br>✅不吃生食或太烫的食物；<br>✅不“口对口”喂饭；<br>✅及时洗手、清洁口腔；<br>✅高危人群应定期体检。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hlfb5tdx2fj20hs0dfgma.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 07:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
